 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alessi-Rose.-Credit-Phoebe-Lettice-Thompson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alessi-Rose.-Credit-Phoebe-Lettice-Thompson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alessi-Rose.-Credit-Phoebe-Lettice-Thompson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alessi-Rose.-Credit-Phoebe-Lettice-Thompson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Alessi-Rose">阿莱西·罗斯（Alessi Rose）</a>以她多情的新单曲“Start All Over”拉开了新的一年的序幕。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/alessi-rose-singer-interview-eat-me-alive-radar-3610809">与阿莱西·罗斯 (Alessi Rose) 一起打保龄球，他是超混乱和自白流行音乐的捍卫者</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌由乔什·斯卡布罗 (Josh Scarbrow) 制作，罗斯·霍伯特 (Rose) 和奥黛丽·霍伯特 (Audrey Hobert) 作词，以柔和、乡村风格的吉他连复段开头，然后很快进入流行节奏。</p><p> <em>“不要表现得好像你不知道/除非你成功，否则不会有第一步/我很随波逐流，但是/除非你采取行动，否则我会砍掉我的手“他们，”</em>罗斯唱道，详细描述了她对暗恋对象的感受，希望他们能采取行动。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="阿莱西·罗斯 - 从头开始​​（歌词）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u_YfVH3c5Lk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，这位德比歌曲作者分享道：“《Start All Over》讲述的是当你开始喜欢某人，但没有人真正愿意为此做任何事情的时候。这很有趣、厚颜无耻、善解人意，但也令人心碎，因为你无休止地希望对方迈出第一步”</p><p> 《Start All Over》是她之前发行的歌曲《Pretty World》、《Imsochillandcool》和《Oh My》的后续作品，也是她即将于 1 月 17 日通过 AWAL 发行的 EP《For Your Validation》的最终预览。您可以<a href="https://alessirose.ffm.to/startallover?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaYKsLL3imBDV61Q2V4_CPhzipU1TtqevrlZECeHSMwFWvYba9mu8l53Fas_aem_0G_0ktlleVHMlOn_Hi0ErA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预先保存。</p><p> Rose 还将于今年春天晚些时候开始她的 2025 年“For Your Validation”英国、爱尔兰和欧洲巡演。查看下面的完整日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Falessi-rose-tickets%2Fartist%2F5444138" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DB_E3HNoPnE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 54